1. Enable i2c on the Raspberry Pi
   sudo raspi-config
Then go to Interface Options → I2C → Enable

2. reboot to reset and update
  sudo reboot

3. Verify i2c is enabled and working:
  sudo apt install -y i2c-tools
  sudo i2cdetect -y 1

4. Library Installation for the ADC and Sensor
  sudo pip3 install adafruit-circuitpython-mprls
  sudo pip3 install adafruit-blinka adafruit-circuitpython-ads1x15